        <abstract> 
<p>Dissection of <hi rend="italic">Leschenaultia</hi> convinces CD insect agency necessary for <hi rend="italic">self</hi>-fertilisation in this case.</p> 
            <p>Primroses and cowslips seem universally to occur in two forms. Very curious to see which plants set seed.</p>
